room_title: Escape room "Cemetery Eterna" by The Art of Escape: ICT in Wichita
room_description: The Witching hour has come, and you and your team have decided you're going treasure hunting. There's a cemetery down the street, and rumor has it that great treasures lie within. You'll have one hour to escape with the treasure before the Crypt Keeper makes his rounds... Do you have the guts to delve into the graves of the departed and open the giant Crypt in the middle of the forest?
